    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-12-06T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-12-06T13:00:00-05:00" n="180"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d180">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">810.20 Defense/422: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Daniels</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-12-06T12:00:00-06:00"
                            >December 6, 1940—noon.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 5 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>406. For the Under Secretary. Your 367, November 26, 9 p.m. Ambassador Castillo
                    Nájera, who has undertaken to discuss the question of the date and nature of the
                    joint announcement regarding the Joint Mexican-American Defense Commission with
                    President Avila Camacho says that he hopes to have something to tell us in a day
                    or two.</p>
                <p>The Ambassador has inquired whether you have any views regarding the place where
                    the commission might first meet and whether this should be included in the
                    announcement. Would you kindly telegraph me anything on this point which you
                    might wish me to tell him.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Daniels</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
